fm: int brokenCalc(int X, int Y) {         if (X >= Y) return X-Y ;         if ( Y%2 ==0 ) return brokenCalc(X, Y/2) + 1;         return brokenCalc(X, Y+1) + 1;     }
fc: class Solution { public:     int brokenCalc(int X, int Y) {         if (X >= Y) return X-Y ;         if ( Y%2 ==0 ) return brokenCalc(X, Y/2) + 1;         return brokenCalc(X, Y+1) + 1;     } };
